Bafana Bafana's 2-0 loss to Senegal on Friday night smashed hopes the team would qualify for the Russia World Cup in 2018. The equation was simple: win both games, and Bafana Bafana would be on its way to Russia next year. READ: 5 Reasons Why Bafana Bafana Will Always Break Your Heart The South African national team hasn't qualified for a World Cup in 15 years since the 2002 World Cup in Japan/Korea. 


                                                                            


    
